{"tid":447184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝搭地鐵比柱男問候","createTime":"2017-10-25T05:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T05:17:31.000Z","uid":76825,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e26f0da2e98444889e2484feb981aacee194d716","tid":447184,"uid":76825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:05:50.000Z","msg":"今朝搭地鐵遇上柱男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢成個背脊訓埋係柱度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當時我揸緊...<br />\n咁我咪用手指咭佢囉，等佢知我既存在....<br />\n點知佢望一望我，然後開始問候我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話我用拳頭打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢對話左一陣，比佢爆粗問候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左大約30秒，隔離有位男仕好型咁企出黎，企係我前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大聲問候左幾下，柱男收左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後坐埋一邊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rij46dh1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frij46dh1&h=0e93eeaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英雄好低調，落車果時同我眼神對望左，我點頭示意多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好多謝英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宜家呢個香港真係好小。<br />\n希望大家如果見到不公平既事都可以企出黎幫助弱者。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef542fdf5b6bae4679b32b218f030a195150c57","tid":447184,"uid":51933,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:07:52.000Z","msg":"唔洗多謝我<br />\n你唔係我第一個幫過既女仔"},{"pid":"3d69374a5b8d9988b0ce62720bdc3aa2d753c905","tid":447184,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:07:54.000Z","msg":"抄佢牌，扣佢50分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ba83d8c9bf8b96a61457cd7d3133fadbe9ee74","tid":447184,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:07:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14fcd90636265b6d7bfada940c9ba8d99615e4ec","tid":447184,"uid":76825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:11:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇問你拎電話？話今晚爆房？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英雄莫問出處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢無同我講過一句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868d6b6006be9d58640ce0c22e5457e682d04586","tid":447184,"uid":74990,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:14:07.000Z","msg":"咁請問張相係英雄定柱男<br />\n完全無提"},{"pid":"54a7c06a7a5f73759b8138401796f62b741d9264","tid":447184,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁請問張相係英雄定柱男<br />\n完全無提</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa198125e09d8477353ab9235de3960dc51008e","tid":447184,"uid":63202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:16:59.000Z","msg":"咁都好d 幾驚你上黎問我拎電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aed2c019f87d45ef87133eda94accb0ef17d17e","tid":447184,"uid":76825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁請問張相係英雄定柱男<br />\n完全無提</blockquote><br />\n柱男收皮坐低左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d6cddafddbe2f5c3d2fce10c23e01a089a88af","tid":447184,"uid":135529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:17:31.000Z","msg":"連登精神 打救世人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}